More info on how to achieve this look at home using @auntjackiescurlsandcoils below!

To achieve @temsbaby Grammys look, I started by prepping with @auntjackiescurlsandcoils Knot On My Watch Detangler to detangle her hair and add some moisture to it before creating the braids in the front. I then used Don’t Shrink gel on the braids to give it a firm hold. She didn’t want to use a lot of heat on her hair so we used a combination of Curl La La Curl Custard and Quench Leave-In Conditioner to give it a good slip and strong hold. #auntjackies
